normal build:
/Library/Application\ Support/Titanium/sdk/osx/1.2.0.RC3/tibuild.py -d . -t bundle -j -p PACKAGE -r Gtasktic/

Build for store:

1. Build package

sudo /Library/Application\ Support/Titanium/sdk/osx/1.2.0.RC3/tibuild.py -d . -t bundle -j -p PACKAGE -n --appstore Gtasktic/

2. chmod the permissions
sudo chmod -R 777 Gtasktic.app

2. Sign package
codesign -f -v -s "3rd Party Mac Developer Application: Ray Wang" Gtasktic.app

3. productbuild package

productbuild --component Gtasktic.app /Applications --sign "3rd Party Mac Developer Installer: Ray Wang" --product Gtasktic.app/Contents/Info.plist Gtasktic.pkg

cat css/dialogs.css css/tipsy.css css/ui.notify.css css/wunderlist.css > alldacss.css

coffee -j all.js --compile app/spine app/spine.model.sqlite app/task app/app
lication app/hotkeys

cat lib/json2.js lib/jquery.tmpl.js lib/jquery.ui.1.8.10.min.js lib/jquery.async.js lib/shortcuts.js lib/encoder.js lib/dateformat.js lib/jquery.notify.min.js > alllibs.js